We value your privacy and are committed to protecting your personal information. This Privacy Policy explains how the Michigan Specialties extension ("we," "our," or "us") collects, uses, and safeguards your information.

Information We Collect
User Preferences:

We collect and store your category preferences (Food, Goods, Souvenirs) to enhance your user experience. This allows the extension to remember your last selected category and provide quicker access to relevant specialties.
Cached Data:

We cache specialty data locally on your device to improve load times and ensure the extension can function offline. This data includes the list of specialties and their details.
How We Use Your Information
Personalization: We use your stored preferences to personalize the content displayed by the extension, providing a more tailored experience.
Performance: Cached data is used to enhance the performance and responsiveness of the extension, ensuring that you can access information quickly and efficiently.
Information Sharing and Disclosure
No Sharing with Third Parties: We do not share, sell, or distribute your personal information to third parties.
Local Storage Only: All information collected by the extension is stored locally on your device and is not transmitted to our servers or any external entities.
Security
We implement reasonable security measures to protect the information stored locally on your device. However, please be aware that no method of electronic storage is 100% secure, and we cannot guarantee absolute security.

Your Choices
Managing Preferences: You can clear your stored preferences and cached data at any time by uninstalling the extension or through your browser's settings.
Opt-Out: If you do not wish for your preferences to be stored or data to be cached, you may choose not to use the extension.
Changes to This Privacy Policy
We may update this Privacy Policy from time to time. Any changes will be posted on this page with an updated revision date. We encourage you to review this policy periodically to stay informed about how we are protecting your information.
